---
import SectionWrapper from '../SectionWrapper.astro';
import Button from '../Button.astro';
---
<SectionWrapper id="services" theme="light">
  <!-- Section label -->
  <p class="section-label section-label--light">// 03 WHAT I BUILD</p>

  <!-- Headline -->
  <h2 class="value-headline">I build the operating system your business needs.</h2>

  <!-- Body copy -->
  <div class="value-body">
    <p>
      Not a website. Not an app. Not an AI tool. One system: a clear message
      that explains what you do to a stranger in three seconds, a site that turns
      visitors into leads, and tools that work the way your business actually
      runs.
    </p>

    <p>
      That's your business operating system. When it's built right, it works
      without you holding the pieces together. Clients find you. They understand
      you. They reach out. Your intake runs. Your follow-up goes out. You spend
      your time doing the work, not managing the system that's supposed to
      support it.
    </p>

    <p>
      Most businesses have pieces of this. None of them were designed to work
      together. I design them to work together from the start.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- OK nodes -->
  <ul class="ok-stack" data-animate>
    <li class="ok-node">
      <div class="ok-status">
        <span class="ok-badge">[OK]</span>
        <span class="ok-label">MESSAGE</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ok-desc">
        A clear, plain-language description of what you do, who it's for, and
        why it matters. Strangers understand it in one read.
      </p>
    </li>

    <li class="ok-node">
      <div class="ok-status">
        <span class="ok-badge">[OK]</span>
        <span class="ok-label">SITE</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ok-desc">
        A website that answers the visitor's question before they have to ask
        it: is this the right business for me?
      </p>
    </li>

    <li class="ok-node">
      <div class="ok-status">
        <span class="ok-badge">[OK]</span>
        <span class="ok-label">TOOLS</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ok-desc">
        Software and automation built around how your business actually runs.
        Not around how a software company thinks it should.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Transition + CTA -->
  <div class="value-cta">
    <p class="value-transition">
      // Whether you're starting from scratch or rebuilding what's broken, the diagnostic tells us where to begin.
    </p>
    <Button variant="primary" href="/diagnostic">[GET YOUR FREE DIAGNOSTIC &gt;]</Button>
  </div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  /* Headline - Geist Sans */
  .value-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    max-width: var(--measure-wide);
  }

  /* Body copy */
  .value-body {
    max-width: var(--measure-normal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .value-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .value-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* OK stack */
  .ok-stack {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .ok-node {
    border: 2px solid var(--text);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--bg-light);
  }

  /* OK status line */
  .ok-status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .ok-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--success);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .ok-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* OK description */
  .ok-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: var(--measure-normal);
  }

  /* CTA area */
  .value-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .value-transition {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    max-width: var(--measure-normal);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-3);
    }

    .value-cta {
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .value-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }
  }
</style>
